Gitorious Merge Request Monitor
- A simple service for following the status of Gitorious merge requests.

Currently supports reporting status over IRC.

Author: Jon Nordby
License: GPLv3+

== Dependencies ==
Python 2.x
Twisted
feedparser

== Usage ==
From source tree:

 export PYTHONPATH=./
 ./bin/gitorious-mrq-monitor myproject

Install and use:

 python setup.py install
 gitorious-mrq-monitor myproject

See --help for more options.

